snippet.title: Mecha BREAK | Official Gameplay Trailer—Take Part in Closed Alpha Test!
snippet.description:
Warning! We're breaching Earth's gravity! Stabilize your mecha! Adjust thrusters and initiate descending protocol now! Show me what you've got, Alysnes... This footage is from the in-development tutorial and actual gameplay recordings. Please note that it is not a finalized version. #MechaBREAK
